videos.description: Maryland pooches the kickoff and regains possession in Rutgers territory.
videos.headline: Maryland recovers 'long onside kick'

videos.description: Maryland defense comes up with a big interception on Artur Sitkowski in Rutgers territory.
videos.headline: Maryland defense picks off Sitkowski

videos.description: Kasim Hill locates Taivon Jacobs  and throws a 23-yard touchdown pass on the run.
videos.headline: Hill connects with Jacobs for the 23-yard Maryland TD

videos.description: Maryland's Ty Johnson takes the hanoff, bounces off defenders and navigates his way 39 yards down field for a big gain.
videos.headline: Johnson breaks out for huge 39-yard run for Terrapins

videos.description: Kasim Hill connects with Tayon Fleet-Davis for a 20-yard touchdown pass putting Maryland up over Rutgers 24-0.
videos.headline: Hill throws his second TD for Terrapins

videos.description: Artur Sitkowski's pass is tipped and intercepted by the Terrapins defensive line.
videos.headline: Maryland defense hauls in second INT on Sitkowski

videos.description: Tino Ellis comes up with the third interception of the day for the Terrapins and returns it 44 yards into Rutgers territory.
videos.headline: Sitkowski throws third INT of the day

videos.description: Kasim Hill locates Jeshaun Jones with an 8-yard touchdown pass putting Maryland up over Rutgers 34-0.
videos.headline: Hill finds Jones for 8-yard Maryland TD

videos.description: Darnell Savage Jr. comes up with the fourth Maryland interception of the day on Rutgers quarterback Artur Sitkowski.
videos.headline: Sitkowski throws fourth INT to Maryland defense

videos.description: Giovanni Rescigno's pass is snatched away by Tre Watson giving the Maryland defense its fifth interception of the day.
videos.headline: Maryland defense hauls in fifth INT of the day
